  "title": "Campaign Management Trainee ⚡️",
  "description": "<p>Altius Organization is a company appointed by local and international clients from diversified industries to build their marketing presence and services<br /></p><p>We are seeking a driven and ambitious Campaign Management Trainee to join our sales and marketing team<br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Acquire and implement strategies to expand consumer base</li><li>Leading team and sales projects to meet client objectives</li><li>Oversee the performance of marketing events and outreach</li><li>Review the effectiveness of strategies according to campaign targets</li><li>Assist with overall support to the team and identify ways to facilitate progression</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Goal-oriented and process-driven mentality</li><li>Self-motivated with a creative character</li><li>A business mindset, passion for achieving as part of an excelling team</li><li>Attitude to contribute and develop alongside the company</li><li>Passport ready</li></ul><p>If you are looking forward to working with some of the leading establishments in the international market, here is your opportunity to kickstart a career in the sales and marketing field!</p>",
